b0b6cef5" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
proxy statement last year</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=
Resolved: Shareholders request that ExxonMobil, with board oversight, publi=
sh a report, omitting proprietary information and prepared at reasonable co=
st, assessing the public health risks of expanding petrochemical operations=
 and investments in areas increasingly prone to climate change-induced stor=
ms, flooding, and sea level rise.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px =
0;">That was proposed by =E2=80=9Cthe Park Foundation, a client of As You S=
ow, ... the beneficial owner of 117 shares.=E2=80=9D If shareholders had vo=
ted for this proposal,=C2=A0the effect would have been that, uh, Exxon=E2=
=80=99s shareholders would have requested that report. It is what is called=
 a nonbinding (or =E2=80=9Cprecatory=E2=80=9D)=C2=A0shareholder proposal, a=
nd Exxon=E2=80=99s board and managers could have said =E2=80=9Cwe appreciat=
e the request but we have decided not to prepare that report.=E2=80=9D</p><=
p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Or Exxon=C2=A0could have prepared a report and =
then kept doing what it was doing. The nonbinding request was not =E2=80=9C=
stop expanding petrochemical operations in areas prone to climate change-in=
duced storms=E2=80=9D or whatever; it was =E2=80=9Cwrite a report.=E2=80=9D=
 The report could have said =E2=80=9Cmeh oil drilling is fine, we=E2=80=99r=
e gonna keep doing it,=E2=80=9D or it could have said =E2=80=9Cactually the=
re are some significant risks, but we=E2=80=99re gonna keep doing it.=E2=80=
=9D The shareholder proposal did not ask Exxon to change its business, just=
 to write a report about it.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ultimately onl=
y about 24.5% of Exxon=E2=80=99s shareholders <a href=3D"https://link.mail.=
bloombergbusiness.com/click/23970292.271103/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9=
